description:
The European Branch (or simply Headquarters), located in England, is one of the seven branches of the http://anidb.net/ch32498 [Black Order] and is the main branch, overseen by Branch Chief and Chief Officer http://anidb.net/ch7365 [Komui Lee] and his sister, Chief Assistant http://anidb.net/ch7123 [Lenalee Lee]. Recently, Lenalee was replaced as the Chief Assistant by http://anidb.net/ch83417 [Bridget Faye].
Source: D.Gray-man Wiki, edited.
